answers.body_markdown:
You need to specify the Maven artifact containing the annotation processor using `&lt;annotationProcessorPaths&gt;`, e.g.:

```xml
&lt;plugin&gt;
    &lt;groupId&gt;org.apache.maven.plugins&lt;/groupId&gt;
    &lt;artifactId&gt;maven-compiler-plugin&lt;/artifactId&gt;
    &lt;version&gt;3.8.1&lt;/version&gt;
    &lt;configuration&gt;
        &lt;annotationProcessorPaths&gt;
            &lt;annotationProcessorPath&gt;
                &lt;groupId&gt;com.example&lt;/groupId&gt;
                &lt;artifactId&gt;com.example.annotations&lt;/artifactId&gt;
                &lt;version&gt;0.0.1-SNAPSHOT&lt;/version&gt;
            &lt;/annotationProcessorPath&gt;
        &lt;/annotationProcessorPaths&gt;
        &lt;annotationProcessors&gt;
            &lt;annotationProcessor&gt;com.example.annotations.MyProcessor&lt;/annotationProcessor&gt;
        &lt;/annotationProcessors&gt;
    &lt;/configuration&gt;
&lt;/plugin&gt;
```

Source: https://maven.apache.org/plugins/maven-compiler-plugin/compile-mojo.html#annotationProcessorPaths

